Note: Paperwork will not be mailed to the buyer until 1-2 months after the auction. This vehicle has a payoff and the lien holder will release the title to the bankruptcy trustee to sign. Certificate of Title, Transfer Form, and Court Order will be mailed once 1. the court order is received and 2. the title has been released by lienholder and signed by the bankruptcy trustee. Please allow several weeks after the removal. Thank you for your patience. The Bidder shall not bid on behalf of another individual; the Bidder/Purchaser/DMV Registrant must be the same. The Buyer is fully responsible for all aspects of smog, registration, transfer, sales tax, and fees due to the DMV.

**Handicap Plates: Per DMV, the handicap plates will be removed as they are tied to the registered owner and not the vehicle. The Buyer will need to apply for new license plates. The new owner will be given new plates when they register the vehicle in their name.Â
